data.description: This beautiful turnkey condo is nestled in the heart of the ever-popular Rino District of Denver! Enjoy the expansive city views from your private balcony, the natural light that floods the home through the large windows/ sliding glass doors, and the open concept living space throughout the unit. The Rino District offers breweries, art, restaurants, coffee shops, and public transportation out your front door. This unit sits on the 2nd floor of the complex in a gated community and offers one reserved parking space. Come check out all that this unit has to offer.
